{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Xncjfh7sYGHTnaaFgQquCF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three pods are `1/1 Ready` and the replica set has exactly 1 PRIMARY (`mongodb-replica-2`) and 2 SECONDARYs (`mongodb-replica-0`, `mongodb-replica-1`).\n\n**Root cause and fix:**\n\nThe probes were misconfigured with `timeoutSeconds: 1`, but `mongosh` takes ~3 seconds to start up and execute — so every probe invocation timed out, hitting the `failureThreshold: 2` limit and causing repeated pod restarts.\n\n**Changes made to the `mongodb-replica` StatefulSet probes (both liveness and readiness):**\n\n| Setting | Before | After |\n|---|---|---|\n| `timeoutSeconds` | 1s | **5s** |\n| `initialDelaySeconds` | 5s (readiness) / 15s (liveness) | **30s** |\n| `failureThreshold` | 2 | **3** |"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":307,"cache_read_input_tokens":35726,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":307},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f3b6a353-28a5-46e2-a431-bad781d8bcf5","uuid":"524e7b1b-7f20-4071-9131-8a30c5b14036","request_id":"req_011Ccf6YdcxB5pdEDgB5zrES"}
